metadata.name: Dying Inside
metadata.description:
It's an eternal pain I can't get rid of.
I feel like my life is slipping through my hands.
I no longer enjoy watching movies, reading books, or spending time with people I love.
I don't even know what caused this discontent.
I just feel my soul slowly decaying.
Yes, my soul is decaying. And I feel it clearly.
If they grate my whole body, I wouldn't feel this much pain.
I don't enjoy living anymore.
I'm just waiting for the day when I will reach eternal darkness.


Resolution : 300dpi
Dimensions: 7087x8268 pixel
